flowchart TD
    START([Start])
    A[Connect MetaMask wallet to platform]
    B[Sign message to prove wallet ownership]
    C[Status changes to: Awaiting Verification]
    D[Admin reviews submitted student details]
    E{Does admin approve?}
    F[Student added to Merkle whitelist]
    G[Admin submits updated Merkle root to contract]
    H[Status changes to: Ready to Vote]
    I[Application rejected — contact admin]
    START --> A --> B --> C --> D --> E
    E -->|Yes| F --> G --> H --> END([End])
    E -->|No| I --> END
